Over the course of a release, various small bugs get discovered that can be fixed by a patched JSP or class.  Typically these patches are attached to a jira.atlassian.com bugreport, and users can download and apply the change locally.  It would be nice to have a patch system, whereby approved patches can be automatically downloaded and applied.

A simple Ant-based system is described at:

http://aft.sourceforge.net/updates.html

